Class DBSTypeHandle

java.lang.Object
  DBSTypeHandle
public class DBSTypeHandle
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides a simple way to see how different types interact with each other. All types are available as final variables, and all variables and functions are static, so you should never have to allocate one of these objects. Which is good, because it's a fairly large array...

Version:
0.1 Java
Author:
